
Kaalam tadabadene,
Ponge keratamulagene,
Praanam parugulai,
Kalugullo doorele.
Dooke dhairyama jaagratha,
Pove po etukaina,
Devara mungita neeventa,
Povenduke devara.
Jagatiki chetu cheyanela,
Devara vetukandanela,
Padame kadamai digite,
Fela fela.
Kanuluka kanarani leela,
Kadaliki kaapayindivela,
Vidhike edurai velite,
Vila vila.
Alalayee erupu neelle,
Aa kallanu kadigera,
Pralayamai atadi raake,
Dada dada dandonora.
Devara mauname,
Savarna leni hechcharika,
Ragilina kopame,
Mrutyuvukaina mucchemata.
Dooke dhairyama jaagratha,
Raake tegabadi raake,
Devara mungita nuvvemtha,
Daakove .
Kaalam tadabadene,
Ponge keratamulaagene,
Praanam parugulai,
Kalugullo doorele.
Dooke dhairyama jaagratha,
Pove po etukaina,
Devara mungita neeventa,
Povenduke devara.
Devara   
by rooshan chowdar
